ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T18:02:07.000Z","msg":"各社交平台都冇咩人宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"暫時見badges story<br />\nremembrance day hong kong <br />\n加拿大領事館<br />\n呢幾個page有提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"但好少有中文版，同埋冇乜背景資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac332393c233b5d48adee4aeb729fd6a12bbfe77","tid":890060,"uid":30215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T03:30:19.000Z","msg":"The Poppy Appeal in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nPoppies can be obtained at the following locations:<br />\n<br />\nFrom Tuesday 30th October 2018 - our Temporary Poppy Depot at Suite 607-608, Gloucester Tower, 15 Queen's Road Central, Hong Kong. (Tel : 2955 7833)<br />\n<br />\nOpening hours:  Mondays-Fridays 9am-5pm (including lunchtimes)<br />\n<br />\nFriday 9th and Saturday 10th November 2018:  Charity Booth in Pacific Place (opposite the walkway to Queensway)<br />\n<br />\nSaturday 10th November 2018 - Poppy Day. Volunteers meet between 8am to 10am at the Depot shown above<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">The streets of Hong Kong from 9am - 12:15pm.  Please note our permit allows us to sell on the Streets of <strong>Hong Kong Island</strong> Only.</span>"},{"pid":"1f5db48a9adedb1e82b3fae9dcb2713f98c16569","tid":890060,"uid":196445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T18:44:19.000Z","msg":"想問過咗11月11號，仲可唔可以載？"}]}